          "settings": {
            "heading": "International",
            "icon": "check_mark",
            "row_content": "<p>We love working with retailers around the world!<br/><br/>Please complete the international application <a href=\"https://bayandstew.com/pages/wholesale-signup-form-outside-us\" title=\"https://bayandstew.com/pages/wholesale-signup-form-outside-us\"><strong>here.</strong><br/></a><br/><strong>To apply, please provide:</strong></p><ul><li>Business registration or license</li><li>VAT number or Sales Tax Permit Number / Resale Number (if applicable)</li><li>Proof of business (website, storefront, or social presence)</li></ul>",
